        "content": "WF-05 Availability + Conflict + Time Zone Check\n\nPurpose:\nEvaluate executive availability, attendee overlap, time-zone correctness, duration reasonableness, and hard/soft conflict state.\n\nCoverage:\n- Boss availability\n- Required attendee availability\n- Optional attendee impact\n- Time-zone validation\n- Duration validation\n- Conflict detection\n- Double-booking and recurring conflict signal\n- Stop or continue status",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 340,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "sticky_wf05_intro",
      "name": "Sticky Note - WF-05 Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [20, 40]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "keepOnlySet": false,
        "values": {
          "string": [
            {
              "name": "wf_name",
              "value": "WF-05 Availability + Conflict + Time Zone Check"
            },
            {
              "name": "status",
              "value": "IN_PROGRESS"
            },
            {
              "name": "status_log_wf05_01",
              "value": "WF-05 started availability, time-zone, and conflict analysis."
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "set_wf05_start",
      "name": "Set - Start WF-05",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [420, 340]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "calendar": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "primary",
          "mode": "list",
          "cachedResultName": "primary"
